---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="home - nick909">
	<main class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
		<h1 class="font-bold text-3xl py-3">Hi 👋</h1>
		<p>i am nick909, a student and developer in Milan, Italy 🇮🇹</p>
		<h1 class="font-bold text-3xl py-3">What i like/dislike</h1>
		<p>i like a lot of things, such as:</p>
		<ul class="favlist">
			<li>IT and tech in general 💻</li>
			<li>football ⚽ (favorite teams are: AC Milan, Real Madrid and SSC Napoli)</li>
			<li>taking pictures 📸</li>
			<li>hanging out with friends</li>
			<li>collecting game consoles and emulating them (legally 😏)</li>
		</ul>
		<p>what i don't like is anything that's not in the list lmao</p>
		<h1 class="font-bold text-3xl py-3">Coming soon 👀</h1>
		<p>i'm planning to add a blog section and a history page so you can learn the evolution of this website and the most painful attempts it took me to perfection it (i need time y'all 🥲)</p>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Unbounded:wght@200..900&display=swap");
	body {
		@apply flex h-screen;
		padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
		font-family: "Unbounded", sans-serif;
	}

	.underline-2 {
		border-bottom: 1px solid;
	}

	.favlist {
		list-style: inside;
	}
</style>
